 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ 카카오톡 오픈빌더 신청하기 ]</h2>\n<p>  <strong>키카오톡 오픈빌더</strong>를 통해서 카카오 챗봇을 제작할 수 있습니다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2ba1c4f264907a390555861d29961025/52c43/kakao_chatbot_openbuilder_login.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 63.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kakao chatbot openbuilder login\"\n        title=\"kakao chatbot openbuilder login\"\n        src=\"/static/2ba1c4f264907a390555861d29961025/c1b63/kakao_chatbot_openbuilder_login.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2ba1c4f264907a390555861d29961025/5a46d/kakao_chatbot_openbuilder_login.png 300w,\n/static/2ba1c4f264907a390555861d29961025/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_openbuilder_login.png 600w,\n/static/2ba1c4f264907a390555861d29961025/c1b63/kakao_chatbot_openbuilder_login.png 1200w,\n/static/2ba1c4f264907a390555861d29961025/52c43/kakao_chatbot_openbuilder_login.png 1499w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://i.kakao.com/login\">카카오톡 오픈빌더</a>에 접속해 왼쪽의 <strong>카카오톡 채널 챗봇 만들기</strong>를 선택하여 로그인하고 신청합니다. (신청 후 일정 기간이 지나면 승인됩니다.)</p>\n<h2 id=\"-채널-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%B1%84%EB%84%90-\" aria-label=\" 채널  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ 채널 ]</h2>\n<p>  챗봇을 사용하려면 챗봇을 연결할 <strong>채널</strong>이 필요합니다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 832px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e8979e96c7e5dfa5665589837ec51cee/ef6b9/kakao_chatbot_make_channel.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kakao chatbot make channel\"\n        title=\"kakao chatbot make channel\"\n        src=\"/static/e8979e96c7e5dfa5665589837ec51cee/ef6b9/kakao_chatbot_make_channel.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e8979e96c7e5dfa5665589837ec51cee/5a46d/kakao_chatbot_make_channel.png 300w,\n/static/e8979e96c7e5dfa5665589837ec51cee/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_make_channel.png 600w,\n/static/e8979e96c7e5dfa5665589837ec51cee/ef6b9/kakao_chatbot_make_channel.png 832w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 832px) 100vw, 832px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>  <a href=\"https://center-pf.kakao.com/\">카카오톡 관리자 센터</a>에 접속해 채널을 생성해 줍니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"-챗봇-만들기-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%B1%