/>\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>  승인이 되었다면 <a href=\"https://i.kakao.com/openbuilder\">카카오톡 오픈빌더</a>에 접속하여 <strong>+</strong>를 눌러 카카오 챗봇을 만들어 줍니다.  </p>\n<h2 id=\"-시나리오-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%8B%9C%EB%82%98%EB%A6%AC%EC%98%A4-\" aria-label=\" 시나리오  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ 시나리오 ]</h2>\n<p>  <strong>시나리오</strong>는 카카오 챗봇에서 제공하는 여러 <strong>블록</strong>들로 구성된 서비스 단위입니다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1e9381707cda6f7c1a4e94806afffb23/d9199/kakao_chatbot_make_senario.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 97.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kakao chatbot make senario\"\n        title=\"kakao chatbot make senario\"\n        src=\"/static/1e9381707cda6f7c1a4e94806afffb23/d9199/kakao_chatbot_make_senario.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e9381707cda6f7c1a4e94806afffb23/5a46d/kakao_chatbot_make_senario.png 300w,\n/static/1e9381707cda6f7c1a4e94806afffb23/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_make_senario.png 600w,\n/static/1e9381707cda6f7c1a4e94806afffb23/d9199/kakao_chatbot_make_senario.png 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>블록</strong><br>\n<strong>블록</strong>은 대화의 최소단위로 <strong>사용자 발화 - 봇 응답</strong>으로 구성되어 있습니다.  </li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>블록 제작하기</strong><br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1142px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dce824a5319eebfdb0bef0f903d0af77/b490f/kakao_chatbot_user_talk.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.333333333333332%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kakao chatbot user talk\"\n        title=\"kakao chatbot user talk\"\n        src=\"/static/dce824a5319eebfdb0bef0f903d0af77/b490f/kakao_chatbot_user_talk.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dce824a5319eebfdb0bef0f903d0af77/5a46d/kakao_chatbot_user_talk.png 300w,\n/static/dce824a5319eebfdb0bef0f903d0af77/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_user_talk.png 600w,\n/static/dce824a5319eebfdb0bef0f903d0af77/b490f/kakao_chatbot_user_talk.png 1142w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1142px) 100vw, 1142px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>블록에서 사용자가 입력할 것 같은 <strong>발화를 등록</strong>해줍니다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 843px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/44e4048d484d1ea9c33b17f2fd1b5616/4ff83/kakao_chatbot_response_buttons.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kakao chatbot response buttons\"\n        title=\"kakao chatbot response buttons\"\n        src=\"/static/44e4048d484d1ea9c33b17f2fd1b5616/4ff83/kakao_chatbot_response_buttons.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/44e4048d484d1ea9c33b17f2fd1b5616/5a46d/kakao_chatbot_response_buttons.png 300w,\n/static/44e4048d484d1ea9c33b17f2fd1b5616/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_response_buttons.png 600w,\n/static/44e4048d484d1ea9c33b17f2fd1b5616/4ff83/kakao_chatbot_response_buttons.png 843w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 843px) 100vw, 843px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>그리고 <strong>텍스트, 카드, 스킬</strong> 등을 이용하여 해당 발화에 대한 <strong>응답을 설정</strong>할 수 있습니다.<br>\n<strong>버튼</strong>을 이용하면 다른 블록을 직접 연결하거나 메세지를 전송하도록 하여 다른 블록으로 넘어갈 수 있습니다.  </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>봇 테스트</strong><br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0c40ecb4adc13ea29b88d2e0c9bc1fd5/5a791/kakao_chatbot_bot_test.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kakao chatbot bot test\"\n        title=\"kakao chatbot bot test\"\n        src=\"/static/0c40ecb4adc13ea29b88d2e0c9bc1fd5/c1b63/kakao_chatbot_bot_test.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0c40ecb4adc13ea29b88d2e0c9bc1fd5/5a46d/kakao_chatbot_bot_test.png 300w,\n/static/0c40ecb4adc13ea29b88d2e0c9bc1fd5/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_bot_test.png 600w,\n/static/0c40ecb4adc13ea29b88d2e0c9bc1fd5/c1b63/kakao_chatbot_bot_test.png 1200w,\n/static/0c40ecb4adc13ea29b88d2e0c9bc1fd5/5a791/kakao_chatbot_bot_test.png 1248w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>저장하여 등록했다면 오른쪽 상단의 <strong>봇테스트</strong>를 통해서 확인해 볼 수 있습니다.  </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"-기본-시나리오-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%8B%9C%EB%82%98%EB%A6%AC%EC%98%A4-\" aria-label=\" 기본 시나리오  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>&#x3C; 기본 시나리오 ></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>웰컴 블록</strong><br>\n웰컴 블록에서는 봇이 사용자와 처음 채팅을 시작할 때 보여줄 응답을 지정할 수 있습니다.  </li>\n<li><strong>폴백 블록</strong><br>\n폴백 블록에서는 봇이 이해할 수 없는 발화에 대한 응답을 지정할 수 있습니다.  </li>\n<li><strong>탈출 블록</strong><br>\n탈출 블록에서는 대화를 초기화하거나 끝내기 위해 사용할 발화를 지정할 수 있습니다.  </li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"-스킬-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%8A%A4%ED%82%AC-\" aria-label=\" 스킬  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ 스킬 ]</h2>\n<p>  <strong>스킬</strong>은 사용자가 필요로 하는 정보를 <strong>웹 서버</strong>에서 처리하여 제공할 수 있습니다.<br>\n인터넷상에 있어 자주 변하는 정보, 복잡한 연산을 필요로 하는 정보들은 관리자가 직접 등록하기에는 한계가 있습니다. 이런 정보를 스킬을 통해 잘 처리하여 제공할 수 있습니다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0be231a999a9fafc5a0a3cd543cae41a/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_skill_network.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kakao chatbot skill network\"\n        title=\"kakao chatbot skill network\"\n        src=\"/static/0be231a999a9fafc5a0a3cd543cae41a/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_skill_network.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0be231a999a9fafc5a0a3cd543cae41a/5a46d/kakao_chatbot_skill_network.png 300w,\n/static/0be231a999a9fafc5a0a3cd543cae41a/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_skill_network.png 600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>스킬 제작</strong><br>\n스킬 탭에서 스킬을 생성하겠습니다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1194px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0ae7fe862506f2b75d593e9b5566f4e6/187fa/kakao_chatbot_skill.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 65.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kakao chatbot skill\"\n        title=\"kakao chatbot skill\"\n        src=\"/static/0ae7fe862506f2b75d593e9b5566f4e6/187fa/kakao_chatbot_skill.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0ae7fe862506f2b75d593e9b5566f4e6/5a46d/kakao_chatbot_skill.png 300w,\n/static/0ae7fe862506f2b75d593e9b5566f4e6/0a47e/kakao_chatbot_skill.png 600w,\n/static/0ae7fe862506f2b75d593e9b5566f4e6/187fa/kakao_chatbot_skill.png 1194w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1194px) 100vw, 1194px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>URL에 스킬을 제공할 서버의 접속 주소를 입력해줍니다.  </p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"data\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> \n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Googy Bot\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"age\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"1\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위는 스킬 응답 예시입니다. 챗봇과 서버는 <strong>JSON 형식</strong>으로 통신합니다.  </p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>version</strong>: 챗봇이 응답을 이해하는데 필요한 버전입니다. (작성하지 않으면 1.0으로 인식합니다.)  </li>\n<li><strong>data</strong>: 실질적으로 우리가 사용할 응답 데이터입니다.  </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>블록 - 스킬 연결</strong><br>\n스킬 응답을 돌려주는 서버를 만들었다면 이를 블록에서 사용할 수 있습니다.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e426d3c6c58d4f93fd749693a85709bd/4719e/kaka_chatbot_skill_block.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kaka chatbot skill block\"\n        title=\"kaka chatbot skill block\"\n        src=\"/static/e426d3c6c58d4f93fd749693a85709bd/c1b63/kaka_chatbot_skill_block.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e426d3c6c58d4f93fd749693a85709bd/5a46d/kaka_chatbot_skill_block.png 300w,\n/static/e426d3c6c58d4f93fd749693a85709bd/0a47e/kaka_chatbot_skill_block.png 600w,\n/static/e426d3c6c58d4f93fd749693a85709bd/c1b63/kaka_chatbot_skill_block.png 1200w,\n/static/e426d3c6c58d4f93fd749693a85709bd/4719e/kaka_chatbot_skill_block.png 1330w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n<p>그림과 같이 스킬을 지정하면 <strong>{{#webhook.KEY}}</strong>로 스킬 서버에서 받은 데이터를 활용할 수 있습니다.  </p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>스킬 자체 응답 작성하기</strong><br>\n봇 응답을 서버에서 모두 처리하는 방법도 있습니다.<br>\n스킬 서버에서 <strong>template</strong>을 구성해 보내주고 봇 응답으로 <strong>스킬 데이터</strong>를 사용하면 됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"version\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"template\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"outputs\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                <span class=\"token property\">\"basicCard\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                    <span class=\"token property\">\"title\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Skill Test\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                    <span class=\"token property\">\"buttons\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n                        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                          <span class=\"token property\">\"action\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"message\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                          <span class=\"token property\">\"label\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"보기\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n                          <span class=\"token property\">\"messageText\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"보기\"</span>\n                        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n                    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n                <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1053px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/51885410137233fc082943dc2848daf3/34e70/kaka_chatbot_skill_response.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"kaka chatbot skill response\"\n        title=\"kaka chatbot skill response\"\n        src=\"/static/51885410137233fc082943dc2848daf3/34e70/kaka_chatbot_skill_response.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/51885410137233fc082943dc2848daf3/5a46d/kaka_chatbot_skill_response.png 300w,\n/static/51885410137233fc082943dc2848daf3/0a47e/kaka_chatbot_skill_response.png 600w,\n/static/51885410137233fc082943dc2848daf3/34e70/kaka_chatbot_skill_response.png 1053w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1053px) 100vw, 1053px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>  </p>\n</li>\n<li><strong>스킬 파라미터</strong><br>\n스킬에서 <strong>파라미터</strong>를 입력으로 받아 처리한다면 하나의 스킬을 가지고 여러 블록에서 사용할 수 있습니다.  </li>\n</ul>\n<p>  스킬을 위한 <strong>Request, Reponse</strong>에 대한 자세한 내용은 카카오의 [<a href=\"https://i.kakao.com/docs/skill-response-format\">응답 타입별 JSON 포맷</a>] 문서를 참고하시면 좋을 것 같습니다.  </p>\n<h2 id=\"-more-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-more-\" aria-label=\" more  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>[ MORE ]</h2>\n<p>  지금까지 기본적인 기능을 제공할 수 있는 카카오톡 챗봇을 제작해보았습니다.<br>\n카카오 오픈빌더에는 더 많은 기능들이 있으니 더 공부하실 분은 [<a href=\"https://i.kakao.com/docs/getting-started-overview\">오픈 빌더 가이드</a>]를 참조하시길 바랍니다.  </p>"},"primaryTag":{"name":"project","color":"#007acc"}},"pageContext":{"postId":"3ec7c318-9387-5696-90dc-b3ee319f8cf8","primaryTag":"project"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1116962356","1994268275","2206391224","2275848304","545095672"]}